msgid ""
"A preset called '%1' is already in the gallery. Rename your preset (Manage… "
"→ Rename…) before submitting, so it doesn't collide with the existing entry."
msgstr ""
"Ein Preset namens '%1' ist bereits in der Galerie vorhanden. Benenne dein "
"Preset um (Verwalten… → Umbenennen…), bevor du es einreichst, damit es nicht "
"mit dem vorhandenen Eintrag kollidiert."

msgid ""
"A preset called '%1' is already in the gallery. Rename your preset (Manage… "
"→ Rename…) before submitting."
